<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>gǔ lǎo de qióng cāng 迦南334</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 gǔ lǎo de qióng cāng yī jiù měi tiān yǒu tài yáng, gǔ lǎo de tǔ de yī jiù měi tiān hé miáo zhǎng,
 yǒu rén wèn nǐ yǐ hé wèi yè wǒ men de huí dá shì mù yáng.
 jiān shàng de shǐ mìng nǐ qiān wàn bù néng fàng, zǒu dào nǎ lǐ zhǔ de huà zǒng yào jì xīn shàng,
 shén de ēn diǎn zú gòu wǒ men yòng, zhè jiù shì yī shēng zuì hǎo de liàng guāng.
 zuì hǎo de liàng guāng shì lái zì tiān shàng nà lǐ yǒu shēng mìng quán huó shuǐ zhǎng
 fēng chuī zhōng yuán qiū shōu máng yé hé huá shì wǒ men de lì liàng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>334</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>